{
  "stem": "4284.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were biting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we noticed immediately that an attempt was made to separate men and women.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I stayed on the right side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And all I can remember is my mother, sort of like a hurricane, had taken away, just whooshed away visually, just simply disappeared into a crowd.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "By now, of course, you know, when you're 15 years old, you just simply can't understand what's going on for that moment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And you certainly don't have a life's philosophy to figure things out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You were helpless.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You were confused.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And of course, you were in the crowd of men.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the women were on the other side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And in a tremendously cruel manner, we were forced to march forward.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We marched forward to a building in front of which was an officer, an SS officer, on a-- on a box of two steps, three steps.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And he looked at you, and he pointed with the swagger stick that-- of the men, you go to the right, and the other go to the left.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Meantime, of course, you're looking for your mother, and everybody's looking for family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Occasionally they would see it and wave or recognize, but it was absolute chaos, confusion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "It was the ultimate in panic, which is exactly what the Germans want.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I went to the right, as directed, and many years later found out that was the infamous Dr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Mengele who was making a selection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And you remember the face but no great detail, except when history shows you these things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I was shoved into an adjacent building.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the first thing is we had to take our clothes off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We had to submit to get our hair shaved off.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
